{"tid":1875352,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"佛法治肺炎，有興趣入嚟睇一睇","createTime":"2020-02-11T17:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T06:57:11.000Z","uid":105678,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c09b955d8c9d4c23ea998d290f922a2837b7142d","tid":1875352,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:40:48.000Z","msg":"<strong>佛經定義之病</strong><br />\n<br />\n《摩訶止觀》第八卷〈觀病患境〉：「有身即病。」佛教元素主張色身乃土火風水四大構成，地水火風共相殘害，猶如四蛇同共一篋，即係四大平衡時，身體冇病，當四大失衡就「更互侵毀」。<br />\n<br />\n佛法之事，真係信不信由你，但經書有說：「平健悠悠，徙倚懈怠，若病急時，更轉用心，能辦眾事。又機宜不同，悟應在病。即是四悉檀因緣，應須病患境也。」意即生病係修行人都會有病，甚麼有益於修行，助你心念思察。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>佛法如何治病</strong><br />\n<br />\n《摩訶止觀》特別就坐禪時，如何調整身、心以療病，揭示了六種方法（六治）：止、觀、氣、息、想、術。<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲嚟講，主要運用呼吸法：（十二息：上、下、焦、滿、增長、滅壞、冷、煖、衝、持、和、補）與脣吻吐納的方式；在心法部分，「止」、有「想」、有「觀」。「止」的部分譬如繫心在「臍」，或止心於「丹田」、「足」，或「隨諸病處，諦心止之」<br />\n<br />\n另外仲有想像法：「假想」法譬如「高麗辯師治癭病法，假想此癭如露窠，蜂子在窼須臾蜂子穿窼而出，膿潰膏流蜂子去，眾孔婁婁如空蜂窼，想心成已癭病消差。」非常簡單。<br />\n<br />\n好好運用吐吶法，肺炎不藥而醫。禪定、方術都係治病方式，條條大路通羅馬，大家不妨一試。"},{"pid":"ad8ceed647fcb96c7ce47a0e6579aa9485ae1d5a","tid":1875352,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:42:24.000Z","msg":"Ps. 如是業力致病，唯有聽命接受，不論如何抗拒都會來。行善積德十分重要。"},{"pid":"692ac746acdadf3b37d183cc5eb2b86903f48136","tid":1875352,"uid":191453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d02bb203dd2052faeeaf9d6b11ec7cdf07be84d","tid":1875352,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"692ac746acdadf3b37d183cc5eb2b86903f48136","tid":1875352,"uid":191453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:52:23.000Z","msg":"反正冇害，大家不妨一試"},{"pid":"c891333b8ca9cfe78d902cfb2b43401b96c3d30e","tid":1875352,"uid":159916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:54:50.000Z","msg":"即係點？念力打J ?"},{"pid":"ce52a713add58eb72661c371309154bcdfeb2551","tid":1875352,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:55:24.000Z","msg":"學術台有好多佛學研究者，自從肺炎之後就開始少講討論，相信佢地唔係藏私唔教大家醫病，但希望各位可以一齊弘揚佛法，多多行善。"},{"pid":"9914b9bc45c26e50768e2f968a29369fc3b1bbfb","tid":1875352,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c891333b8ca9cfe78d902cfb2b43401b96c3d30e","tid":1875352,"uid":159916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:54:50.000Z","msg":"即係點？念力打J ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:55:59.000Z","msg":"一字一句寫得好清楚了，跟住吐吶法就可以修練"},{"pid":"2f46627465eaf6b007708165a2287cf3486c2dcc","tid":1875352,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T18:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hvcagbp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHvcagbp.jpg&h=1e272efd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w6B2RJ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw6B2RJ4.jpg&h=2604c676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/StbN2PD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FStbN2PD.jpg&h=874d5396&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MikryXq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMikryXq.jpg&h=76391cc2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"829cb6d638bef758977697c95618faf1c37b39a5","tid":1875352,"uid":15605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T18:09:46.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主，頭先試咗一試，霎那間全身發出金光之後三脈七輪全部打開咗，聽日唔洗再周圍撲口罩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3439b24ff9870f9e4960c2375267f9d18b936c37","tid":1875352,"uid":8500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T18:10:44.000Z","msg":"念力抗爭d fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" clas